# Design System & Visual Standards

## Color Palette
- **Primary Background**: Dark theme by default (black/gray tones)
- **Secondary Background**: Subtle gray variations
- **Text**: White/light gray for readability
- **Accent**: Electric blue/neon gradient for highlights
- **Interactive**: Subtle hover states with opacity changes

## Typography
- **Headings**: Modern display font for impact
- **Body**: Clean sans-serif (Inter, Neue Montreal)
- **Hierarchy**: Clear visual distinction between heading levels
- **Line Height**: Generous spacing for readability
- **Font Weights**: Use weight variations for emphasis

## Spacing & Layout
- **Grid System**: Consistent 8px base unit
- **Margins**: Use Tailwind spacing scale consistently
- **Padding**: Generous internal spacing for breathing room
- **Breakpoints**: Mobile-first responsive design
- **Container**: Max-width constraints for optimal reading

## Animation & Interactions
- **Transitions**: Smooth, subtle animations (200-300ms)
- **Hover States**: Micro-interactions with Framer Motion
- **Page Transitions**: Seamless navigation between sections
- **Loading States**: Elegant loading animations
- **Parallax**: Subtle depth effects for premium feel

## Component Standards
- **Buttons**: Consistent styling with hover states
- **Cards**: Subtle shadows and rounded corners
- **Forms**: Clean, accessible input styling
- **Navigation**: Clear, intuitive navigation patterns
- **Icons**: Lucide React icons with consistent sizing

## Accessibility
- **Contrast**: Ensure sufficient color contrast ratios
- **Focus States**: Visible focus indicators
- **Keyboard Navigation**: Full keyboard accessibility
- **Screen Readers**: Proper ARIA labels and semantic HTML
- **Motion**: Respect user's motion preferences
